}

// Line 156-200: Schema Comments and Documentation
//
// GRANDFATHERED PRICING SYSTEM:
// ===============================
// This schema supports individual student pricing through two key fields:
//
// 1. monthlyRate (Float): 
//    - Default: ₱1,400 (current standard rate)
//    - Legacy rates: ₱1,000 (Founding Members), ₱1,200 (Early Adopters)
//    - Yearly rate automatically calculated as monthlyRate * 12
//
// 2. isLegacyStudent (Boolean):
//    - false: Standard pricing (₱1,400/month)
//    - true: Grandfathered pricing (preserved from enrollment date)
//
// PRICING TIERS:
// ==============
// - Founding Members: ₱1,000/month (₱12,000/year) - isLegacyStudent: true
// - Early Adopters: ₱1,200/month (₱14,400/year) - isLegacyStudent: true  
// - Standard Members: ₱1,400/month (₱16,800/year) - isLegacyStudent: false
//
// SMS REMINDER SYSTEM:
// ===================
// The Reminder model tracks all SMS communications:
// - Automatic reminders for overdue memberships (expired within 30 days)
// - Cost tracking for budget management (₱0.35 per SMS)
// - Rate limiting: One reminder per student per 24 hours
// - Phone number validation: Philippine mobile format required
//
// PAYMENT VALIDATION:
// ==================
// Enhanced payment validation ensures amounts match student's individual rates:
// - Monthly payments must equal student's monthlyRate
// - Yearly payments must equal student's monthlyRate * 12
// - Historical payments supported with custom date selection
//
// BACKWARD COMPATIBILITY:
// ======================
// - All existing functionality preserved
// - Default values ensure seamless migration
// - Existing students automatically get standard rates
// - No breaking changes to existing APIs
//
// MIGRATION STEPS:
// ===============
// 1. Update this schema file
// 2. Run: npx prisma db push
// 3. Run: npx prisma generate
// 4. Optionally set legacy students:
//    UPDATE "Student" SET "monthlyRate" = 1000, "isLegacyStudent" = true WHERE id IN (1,2,3);
// 5. Deploy enhanced application code
//
// PERFORMANCE OPTIMIZATIONS:
// =========================
// - Indexed pricing fields for fast queries
// - Efficient SMS lookup by phone number
// - Payment analytics through indexed amounts and dates
// - Membership status queries optimized with compound indexes